    ],
    "abstract": "We introduce formal definitions for deniability in group\r\nchats by extending a pre-existing model that did not have\r\nthis property. We then introduce “epochal signatures” as\r\nan almost drop-in replacement for signatures, which can\r\nbe used to make certain undeniable group-chats deniable\r\nby just performing that replacement. Following that we\r\nprovide a practical epochal signature scheme and prove\r\nits security.",
